data.description: Step into this captivating modern atomic ranch, harmoniously blending mid-century charm with contemporary comfort. Situated in the desirable Bridlewood community just off The Plaza, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven boasts a host of upgrades tailored for effortless living. Revel in the assurance of a new roof and a 2-car garage, complete with a flexible space and full bathroom—perfect for those craving versatility. Outside, the expansive lot offers ample parking, while the brand new roof and HVAC system ensure worry-free enjoyment of this sheer delight!
